From 8cfea0defa2d3e70f2b47da5a23925ec6fa6f7e6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Tomasz=20Paku=C5=82a?= <tomasz.pakula.oficjalny@gmail.com>
