From 95e8f28c7adf01a9174a789dd7ae94c4326b5c3f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Tomasz=20Paku=C5=82a?= <tomasz.pakula.oficjalny@gmail.com>
